    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"ariadne-entry\"><p><strong>Source:</strong> Ariadne's Book of Legends - Alpha v1.2, p. 50-53.</p><p>Body, Mind, Soul (5e)</p><p>5e. When you reach 20th level, increase your Dexterity and Wisdom scores by 4. Your maximum for these ability scores is increased to 25. In addition, you can expend 3 Ki points to bolster yourself against harm for 1 minute or until you have the Incapacitated condition. During that time, you have Resistance to all damage except Force damage.</p></div>",
